introduce_product: BABY-G, the casual watch for active women, announces new Decora style models based on Japanese kawaii culture. The base model is the popular BA110 design dressed up in colors that recall the Decora fashion Harajuku street styles that got their start back in late 1990s. A cool black basic color combined with kitschy, girlish hues for the face and buttons that are inspired by Decora fashions. This new model captures the essence of Japanese fashions that continue to influence cultures around the globe.
list_specification_product:
World Time 
29 time zones (48 cities + UTC), city code display, daylight saving on/off
